        <Parent_String>boxwood (wood) [300012002], hardwood [300011916], wood by composition or origin [300011915], wood (plant material) [300011914], wood and wood by product [300011913], plant material [300124117], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
