    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term used by the lumber trade for firm, close-grained woods that resemble true boxwood but are derived from several other species of tree, including Phyllostylon brasiliensis, Tabebuia pentaphylla, and several species in the genera Eucalyptus and Tristania.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046595/Timbers of the World (1979-1980)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Algemene term die in de houtbranche wordt gebruikt voor stevig hout met een dichte nerfstructuur dat lijkt op echt buxushout, maar afkomstig is van verschillende andere boomsoorten, waaronder Phyllostylon brasiliensis, Tabebuia pentaphylla en verschillende soorten van de geslachten Eucalyptus en Tristania.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>木材貿易業中用於泛指與黃楊木類似，堅實沉重、紋理密實，但其實屬於其他樹種的木材，如巴西葉柱榆木（Phyllostylon brasiliensis）、洋紅風鈴木（Tabebuia pentaphylla），以及桉屬與紅膠木屬的一些樹種。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
